### Import books (raw delimited payload: title|author|publisher, records split by ~)  ->  201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/import
Content-Type: text/plain

Clean Code|Robert Martin|Prentice Hall~Refactoring|Martin Fowler|Addison-Wesley~The Pragmatic Programmer|Andrew Hunt|Addison-Wesley

### List the normalised catalogue  ->  200 OK (JSON array)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### Malformed record (missing fields)  ->  400 Bad Request (ORA-20002)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/import
Content-Type: text/plain

Broken Book|OnlyAuthor

### Empty payload  ->  400 Bad Request (ORA-20001)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/import
Content-Type: text/plain

